Type: Package
Package: ggbrain
Title: Create Images of Volumetric Brain Data in NIfTI Format Using ggplot2 Syntax
Version: 0.8.0
Date: 2022-10-18
Authors@R:
    person("Michael", "Hallquist", , "michael.hallquist@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-5894-8038"))
Maintainer: Michael Hallquist <michael.hallquist@gmail.com>
Description: The ggbrain package provides a ggplot2-consistent approach to generating 2D displays of
  volumetric brain imaging data. The package can display data from multiple NIfTI images and uses standard
  ggplot2 conventions such scales, limits, and themes to control the appearance of displays. The resulting
  plots are returned as patchwork objects, inheriting from ggplot, allowing for any standard modifications
  of display aesthetics supported by ggplot2.
URL: https://michaelhallquist.github.io/ggbrain/
BugReports: https://github.com/michaelhallquist/ggbrain/issues
